== Reception ==
Piousji of ''Sunday'' wrote, "Though Sivaji was rather impressive in the father's role he looked almost silly as the son."<ref name="Sunday">{{Cite magazine |last=Piousji |date=16 November 1980 |title=Khaas Baat |url=https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.99450/page/n327 |magazine=Sunday |page=57}}</ref>

